Nancy Handabile bụ onye Zambia na-eme ihe nkiri, onye nta akụkọ na onye na-eme fim.
Handabile mere ihe ngosi Progress na Love Games, nke nwetara ya nhọpụta maka Best Supporting Actress na 2014 Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards. Ọ duziri Tizibika, ihe ngosi TV nke eziokwu banyere ụmụ nwanyị abụọ na-anwa iji mgbasa ozi mmekọrịta iji nweta aha
Ọ sokwa duzie ma mee ihe nkiri na Zambezi Magic TV show Masauso N'afọ 2019 ọ rụrụ ọrụ na ihe nkiri Zimbabwe Lord of Kush
N'ọnwa Disemba afọ 2018 a matara Handabile dị ka otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị asatọ na-eme ihe nkiri Multi Choice na Southern African Development Community (SADC)

O jiri oge ahụ kpọọ ọtụtụ ụmụ nwanyị ka ha banye n'ọrụ ụmụ nwoke, na maka ime ihe nkiri iji nweta nkwado ego na Zambia. N'ọnwa Mee afọ 2019 ọ natara Ankazi Woman of the Year Award site na Stanbic Bank.
